snippet.title: Free Touhou Fan Game English Version Available Now「 Touhou Hero of Ice Fairy 」
snippet.description:
「 Touhou Hero of Ice Fairy 」is a "Touhou Project" 2D Fan game made of "Horizontal Action"+"Danmaku Bullet hell". In this BOSS RUSH game you play as the beloved Cirno, and embark on her journey to liberate the Gansokyo and save her dear one.

Steam：https://store.steampowered.com/app/1715460/
Patreon：https://www.patreon.com/TouhouGamePulse
Twitter：https://twitter.com/TouhouGamePulse
